Steps:
[NAV] Navigate to {{FRONT_URL}}/sign-in
[ACT] Fill 'Email': {{USER_EMAIL}}
[ACT] Fill 'Password': {{USER_PASSWORD}}
[ACT] Click 'Sign In'
[WAIT] Wait for redirect after successful login
[ASSERT] Capture /connect/token response in network tab

[NAV] Navigate to {{FRONT_URL}}/sign-in
[ACT] Fill 'Email': {{USER_EMAIL}}
[ACT] Fill 'Password': {{USER_PASSWORD}}
[ACT] Click 'Sign In'
[WAIT] Wait for successful login
[ACT] Capture the access_token from /connect/token response
[ACT] Execute fetch to {{BACK_URL}}/api/platform/settings with Authorization: Bearer {customer_token}
[WAIT] Wait for API response
[ASSERT] API returns 401 or 403
[ACT] Execute fetch to {{BACK_URL}}/api/platform/security/users with Authorization: Bearer {customer_token}
[WAIT] Wait for API response
[ASSERT] API returns 401 or 403
[ACT] Execute fetch to {{BACK_URL}}/api/platform/modules with Authorization: Bearer {customer_token}
[WAIT] Wait for API response

[HTTP] POST {{BACK_URL}}/connect/token grant_type=password username=@td(TECHFLOW_ADMIN.email) password=@td(TECHFLOW_ADMIN.password) scope=offline_access storeId={{STORE_ID}}
[WAIT] Receive access_token
[HTTP] POST {{BACK_URL}}/graphql Authorization: Bearer <access_token> body: {"query": "{ me { id email } }"}
[WAIT] Receive GraphQL response (expect me.email to match authenticated user)
